  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>File 47</strong> is not just a game; it’s a window into a shattered mind, an endless echo of a memory that should never have been.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/35a6e7075c4744880e0eb19fce3cad5b.poster.avif?t=1766444578\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/35a6e7075c4744880e0eb19fce3cad5b.webm?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/35a6e7075c4744880e0eb19fce3cad5b.mp4?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this disturbing <strong>psychological survival horror</strong>, you will descend into a nightmare that defies logic and reality. A labyrinth of fragmented memories, endless hallways that transform, and shadows that shouldn’t be there. Every decision matters, every corner hides a secret, and every step could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/6b1b41c989ed85958a867f81896364ee.poster.avif?t=1766444578\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/6b1b41c989ed85958a867f81896364ee.webm?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/6b1b41c989ed85958a867f81896364ee.mp4?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The past cannot be buried, but can you face it? Unravel the dark mysteries of a trauma marked by violence, explore the deepest recesses of the human mind, and search for answers in a world that refuses to give them up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every experience in <i>File 47</i> is unique and random, with events and environments that change with each playthrough. But be careful: after midnight, the game shifts, becoming even more disturbing and pushing the limits of your sanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/fd8272d46979ac246e1bf335b15f0d38.poster.avif?t=1766444578\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/fd8272d46979ac246e1bf335b15f0d38.webm?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/fd8272d46979ac246e1bf335b15f0d38.mp4?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The real question is not what you’ll find at the end, but what you’ll lose along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Are you ready to open the file?</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>File 47</strong> is not just a game; it’s a window into a shattered mind, an endless echo of a memory that should never have been.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/35a6e7075c4744880e0eb19fce3cad5b.poster.avif?t=1766444578\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/35a6e7075c4744880e0eb19fce3cad5b.webm?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/35a6e7075c4744880e0eb19fce3cad5b.mp4?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this disturbing <strong>psychological survival horror</strong>, you will descend into a nightmare that defies logic and reality. A labyrinth of fragmented memories, endless hallways that transform, and shadows that shouldn’t be there. Every decision matters, every corner hides a secret, and every step could be your last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/6b1b41c989ed85958a867f81896364ee.poster.avif?t=1766444578\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/6b1b41c989ed85958a867f81896364ee.webm?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/6b1b41c989ed85958a867f81896364ee.mp4?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The past cannot be buried, but can you face it? Unravel the dark mysteries of a trauma marked by violence, explore the deepest recesses of the human mind, and search for answers in a world that refuses to give them up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every experience in <i>File 47</i> is unique and random, with events and environments that change with each playthrough. But be careful: after midnight, the game shifts, becoming even more disturbing and pushing the limits of your sanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/fd8272d46979ac246e1bf335b15f0d38.poster.avif?t=1766444578\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/fd8272d46979ac246e1bf335b15f0d38.webm?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3479870/extras/fd8272d46979ac246e1bf335b15f0d38.mp4?t=1766444578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The real question is not what you’ll find at the end, but what you’ll lose along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Are you ready to open the file?</i></strong></p>",
